A very basic surf map with 5 differen't surf routes.

###### **Counter-Strike:Source' first rotating skybox!**

Inspired from the Unreal Tournament map 'Facing_Worlds'

This map is protected from decompiling

Only known bug is on 1 ramp which stops your speed (will be fixed in version 2)

Map file - 7MB

- Backround music

- 1 Jail secret
